{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0029_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0029", "six_channel": "太陽病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["傷寒"], "symptoms": ["自汗出", "小便數", "心煩", "微惡寒", "腳攣急", "厥", "咽中乾", "煩躁", "譫語"], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": ["浮"], "prior_treatment": [], "time_course": []}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["調胃承氣湯"], "treatment_principle": ["發汗"], "alternatives": ["甘草乾薑湯", "芍藥甘草湯", "四逆湯"]}, "evidence_span": "傷寒，脈浮，自汗出，小便數，心煩，微惡寒，腳攣急，反與桂枝欲攻其表，此誤也。得之便厥，咽中乾，煩躁吐逆者，作甘草乾薑湯與之，以復其陽。若厥愈足溫者，更作芍藥甘草湯與之，其腳即伸。若胃氣不和，譫語者，少與調胃承氣湯。若重發汗，復加燒針者，四逆湯主之。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為調胃承氣湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「調胃承氣湯」，證據強度：給予（與）。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.82, "prescription_strength": "與", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "warn", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.833, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0070_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0070", "six_channel": "太陽病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": [], "symptoms": ["惡寒", "不惡寒"], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": [], "prior_treatment": ["發汗後"], "time_course": []}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["調胃承氣湯"], "treatment_principle": ["發汗", "和胃氣"], "alternatives": []}, "evidence_span": "發汗後惡寒者，虛故也。不惡寒但熱者，實也。當和胃氣，與調胃承氣湯。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為調胃承氣湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「調胃承氣湯」，證據強度：給予（與）。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.82, "prescription_strength": "與", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.873, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0094_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0094", "six_channel": "太陽病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["太陽病"], "symptoms": ["振慄", "汗出"], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": ["陰陽俱停", "微"], "prior_treatment": ["下之"], "time_course": []}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["調胃承氣湯"], "treatment_principle": ["下之"], "alternatives": []}, "evidence_span": "太陽病未解，脈陰陽俱停，必先振慄汗出而解。但陽脈微者，先汗出而解；但陰脈微者，下之而解。若欲下之，宜調胃承氣湯。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為調胃承氣湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「調胃承氣湯」，證據強度：建議用方（宜）。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.82, "prescription_strength": "宜", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.923, "release_level": "gold"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0105_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0105", "six_channel": "太陽病", "rule_type": "formula_pattern_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["傷寒"], "symptoms": ["譫語", "小便利", "反下利", "自下利", "厥"], "negated_findings": [], "pulse": ["微"], "prior_treatment": ["下之"], "time_course": ["十三日"]}, "then_conclusions": {"formula": ["調胃承氣湯"], "treatment_principle": ["下之"], "alternatives": []}, "evidence_span": "傷寒十三日，過經，譫語者，以有熱也，當以湯下之。若小便利者，大便當硬，而反下利，脈調和者，知醫以丸藥下之，非其治也。若自下利者，脈當微厥，今反和者，此為內實也，調胃承氣湯主之。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "該條可作為調胃承氣湯相關方證的原文證據，原文用語為「調胃承氣湯主之」，證據強度：主治關係（主之）。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.9, "prescription_strength": "主之", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.956, "release_level": "gold"}}
